for more information.  \n  \n## Example  \n The following sample generates C4287:  \n  \n```  \n// C4287.cpp  \n// compile with: /W3  \n#pragma warning(default : 4287)  \n#include <stdio.h>  \n  \nint main()  \n{  \n    unsigned int u = 1;  \n    if (u < -1)   // C4287  \n        printf_s(\"u LT -1\");  \n    else  \n        printf_s(\"u !LT -1\");  \n    return 0;  \n}  \n```"}